<subSubSection box="[199,1015,185,210]" pageId="2" pageNumber="449" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="2.[199,1015,151,210]" box="[199,1015,185,210]" pageId="2" pageNumber="449">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,326,186,210]" pageId="2" pageNumber="449">Discussion.</emphasis>
The new species is similar to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="He, Z. &amp; Gorochov" authorityYear="2017" box="[647,835,185,209]" class="Insecta" family="Gryllidae" genus="Agryllus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="449" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="magnigenitalis">
<emphasis box="[647,663,186,209]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="449">A</emphasis>
